title: Edge_of_Doom_TPB_(2011)_(Digital)_(Monafekk-Empire).cbr
description:
Edge_of_Doom_TPB_(2011)_(Digital)_(Monafekk-Empire) 


Discover the true meaning of terror as fright-masters Steve Niles and Kelley Jones bring you five frightening tales of stark raving horror!

Collecting the five-part mini-series of the same name - Edge of Doom.

What's better than a free comic? A free trade!

Thanks to IDW Publishing, Kelley Jones and Steve Niles, the entire trade is available as free downland (in PDF format) on the creator's homepage. The free download was made available by Niles in November 2012.
